       Hell Beast arrived at the base, and him and his men made it inside 
through a small side entrace that droped a small zone of the shiled and 
closed it agian once the Predacon force was inside.
       "Tarantulas! I want those jets out of the sky, and those idiots on the 
jet packs blown apart!" He bellowed. Tarantulas responded by sending out 
several more cluster missles and autogun fire.
       "And now, for Killfests base. Look at this strategy and let me know 
what you think. Then, the volunteers can go."
